00:03:18.120 --> 00:03:26.440
where we had eight days of attacks against black people by a white mob and all of these riots

00:03:26.440 --> 00:03:31.960
were white mobs attacking black and minority people. In Liverpool the most notable and for

00:03:31.960 --> 00:03:38.760
many people was the event of Charles Wooden being pursued by a crowd of thousands beaten and thrown

